Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是羞死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然要脫的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一口氣全都脫光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…她說了脫衣舞對吧  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容變得越來越刺激了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次大概也是另一個自己在肆意妄為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理瀨果然在電視裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又沒能阻止犯人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都知道犯人的目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之明天再說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家忘了熊熊  只顧自己開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊被拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既無聊又自卑啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在比起這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這種事情」是什麼意思啊熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正熊熊只是一隻連自己是什麼都不知道的沒用熊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾什麼滾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既找不到答案  大家也不來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  我有件事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為寂寞我想試著哭一下  但是哭不出來啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自一熊的話就會想這想那的  寂寞感成倍增長中熊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼會忘記你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們時不時地會想起你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天你可以倒貼給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒貼的捏它能不能不要再用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  有沒有個叫做久慈川理瀨的孩子進到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久慈川理瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理瀨在這裡面？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣味很強烈熊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉街或者那種旅館裡必有的那種地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我家裡可沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  完二同學還沒有得到眼鏡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是弄錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太相稱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有我要戴這種眼鏡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡嗎熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺心跳開始加速了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來裡面是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士們先生們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我將帶領各位前往那美妙的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多…小理瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  我全都看過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身衣服是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小理瀨炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空降日本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久  等  啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小理瀨萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天理瀨將會給大家看個光光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你們說反正是騙人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  OK  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真是假就請親眼確認吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的——我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我當時也是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是要命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是名為理瀨的孩子心中壓抑著的感情熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也沒有注視著真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點冷場了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在這裡有請特別嘉賓登場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉賓？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的嘉賓是——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久慈川理瀨！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  快停下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請遵守規矩  不要對舞娘動手動腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣解決它們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被彈回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就採取肉搏戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒完沒了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實明明非常想讓別人來看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看啊  這就是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下  這樣的人才不是真正的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼真正的你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個才是真正的你？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  眼鏡眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找這個嗎熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍扁你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路碾壓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  說說看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的理瀨究竟是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我  我也是真正的理瀨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂  真正的我究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是真正的理瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對裝出一副糾纏人的小可愛模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要假裝笑臉這種事情我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜大眼睛看清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:09:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾即為影  是為真實的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴上學…長
