Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這隻笨熊  只知道亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  幫上熊忙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何止是幫上忙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我們的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以倒貼給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:14:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊先生為了保護我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道真正的自我是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種痛苦熊熊也很清楚熊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要獨自煩惱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和熊熊一起思考吧熊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師他們也會幫你的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  都是因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不用再勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟有多久沒有聽到這句話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:15:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拼命地思考過了究竟哪張臉才是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這種東西就算去尋找也是找不到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的我不存在於任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的我不存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和小理瀨也全都是我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不能怪她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也已經搖搖晃晃的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很擔心熊熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的我不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在說話啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難  難道說這是另一個熊熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種不協調的感覺是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相永遠都隱藏在你所不知道的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾即為影  是為真實的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也絕無法證明那就是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被吸進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼追尋真相又有何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來連真面目都不知道的東西又要從何找起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為追尋真相  所以你們才會碰上悲慘的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告訴你們一個真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們將會死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙按住卑彌呼  不要讓她被吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑彌呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊邪那岐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑彌呼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.85,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\pos(455,74)\fs15\fsp1\bord0\b1}熊先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.85,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\pos(503,180)\fs15\fsp1\bord0\b1}有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:13.85,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\pos(129,165)\fs15\fsp1\bord0\b1}熊先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了熊先生外裡面還有別的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:22.61,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,74)\fs15\fsp1\bord0\b1}熊先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:22.61,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(539,185)\fs15\fsp1\3cDB00C7\b1}有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  有霧擋著  沒法分析
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這裡是哪裡啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將會消失在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你原本就是虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來就沒有喪失過記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的真面目反正就只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想聽呢熊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要自己去尋找答案熊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此我也要去尋找熊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊雖然裡面是空心的  但也能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想消失熊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和老師他們分別熊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要尋找答案  並置身於更深刻的苦難之中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人費解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了  在胸口再往下一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:34.44,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,74)\fs15\fsp1\bord0\b1}熊先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:34.44,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\pos(510,185)\fs15\fsp1\3cDB00C7\b1}在這裡{\i1}！{\i0}沒有錯{\i1}！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經堅持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊邪那岐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊那自豪的毛色…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之看上去應該沒有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到熊熊也有壓抑著的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊不知道自己是什麼東西熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經覺得或許是找不到答案的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是熊熊現在就在這裡熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活在這裡啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:20:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小理瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起尋找答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊不是孤身一熊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會陪你一起尋找答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大  大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  熊熊真是太幸福了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊也得到了Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能從中感到很強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了啊  熊先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我熊熊就行了熊  小理瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  送到這裡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊倒是一會兒也沒休息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新毛長出來前我要努力鍛鍊身體熊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我華麗地復活之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家能等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力鍛鍊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能來到這個城裡真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有了能做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容身之所？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和你們一起搜捕真正的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠學長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能把這裡也當作容身之所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:00.41,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c000000}人之間的羈絆就是真正的力量
