Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.32,0:24:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太舒服啦熊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.16,0:24:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是很厲害的
